    "Consequently, perception-based research is restricted in its comprehension of the effect.",
    "Future research initiatives using an experiment-based methodological approach might solve this problem.",
    "Finally, a future avenue to pursue is that of exploring potential enhancements to the proposed study model by incorporating moderating variables (e.g., disciplines, age, gender) in order to increase its effectiveness.",
